  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Digivolving] You may trash the top card of your security
    stack to reveal the top 6 cards of your deck. Add up to 2 level 6 or lower Digimon
    cards among them to your hand. Trash the remaining cards.[All Turns][Once Per
    Turn] When a card is removed from your security stack, if you have 3 or fewer
    security cards, trigger \uFF1CRecovery +1 (Deck)\uFF1E. (Place the top card of
    your deck on top of your security stack.)"
